  KiuN-piaN2 Ang-a2. 
  Cha2 u7 chit8 pai2 u7 chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5, kap soe3-han3 e5 lau7 ta-pou-lang5, in ka-ki7 khia7 ti7 chit8 keng soe3 keng ku7 chhu3. In long2 bo5 soe3-han3 cha-bou2 gin2-na2, a2-si7 ta-pou gin2-na2. Sou2-i2 chit8 jit8 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5 eng7 kiuN-piaN2 choe3 chit8 e5 ta-pou gin2-na2; ka7 i choe3 chi-ku-lat8 saN, eng7 jiok8-kui3-chi2 choe3 liu2-a2; bak8-chiu si7 eng7 sui2 koh phauh e5 phu5-to5 choe3; chhui3 eng7 ang5 sek e5 thng5 choe3; iah8 eng7 kam thng5 choe3 chit8 teng2 sui2-sui2 soe3 teng2 e5 bo7-a2. 
  Chit si5 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5 choe3 ho2, chiu7 ka7 i chheng7 saN, iah8 nih8 i e5 kha, chhin-chhiuN7 chheng7 oe5 e5 khoan2-sit, he7 ti7 chit8 e5 poaN5. Au7-lai5 chiu7 chiong chit e5 poaN5 he7 ti7 he2-lou5 ia7 koaiN mng5. I siuN7 ¡§TaN goa2 u7 chit8 e5 goa2 ka-ki7 e5 soe3-han3 ta-pou gin2-na2.¡¨ 
  Kau3 sio ho2 e5 si5, i khui he2-lou5 mng5, thoa chhut chit e5 poaN5. Chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2, ta-pou gin2-na2, thiau3-chhut-lai5 ti7 thou5-kha, iah8 chau2-chhut mng5-khau2 kau3 ti7 koe-lou7 nih8. Chit e5 soe3-han3 lau7 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap chit e5 soe3-han3 lau7 e5 ta-pou-lang5 chiau3 in sou2 oe7 e5 kin2, jip i, chong2-si7 i chhio3 ia7 toa7 siaN kong2, ¡§Chau2, chau2, khoaN3 lin2 oe7 joa7 kin2. Lin2 liah8 goa2 boe7 tioh8, goa2 si7 chit8 e5 kiuN-piaN2 lang5.¡¨ In liah8 i boe7 tioh8. 
  Chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 tit8-tit8 chau2, kau3 ti7 lou7-piN u7 chit8 chiah gu5. 
  Gu5 kong2, ¡§Soe3-han3 kiuN-piaN2 e5 gin2-na2, theng5 ah, Goa2 ai3 chiah8 li2.¡¨ 
  Chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 e5 gin2-na2 chhio3, soa3 kong2, ¡§Goa2 oe7 chau2 li7-khui chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5, kap chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 ta-pou-lang5. Goa2 iah8 oe7 chau2 li7-khui li2, oe7 ouh.¡¨ 
  Hit si5 chit chiah gu5 jip i, i oat8-ke3 khi3 khoaN3, kong2, ¡§Chau2, chau2, khoaN3 li2 oe7 joa7 kin2. Li2 liah8 goa2 boe7 tioh8; goa2 si7 chit8 e5 kiuN-piaN2 lang5.¡¨ 
  Gu5 liah8 i boe7 tioh8. 
  Chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 ta-pou gin2-na2 tit8-tit8 chau2, koh chau2 kau3 chit8 e5 chhau2-tiuN5 u7 chit8 chiah be2. Chit chiah be2 kong2, ¡§ChhiaN2 theng5, soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2, li2 khoaN3 liau2 chin ho2 chiah8.¡¨ 
  Chong2-si7 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 toa7 siaN chhio3, kong2, ¡§Oh ah ! oh ah ! Goa2 oe7 chau2 li7-khui chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5, chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 ta-pou-lang5, koh chit8 chiah gu5. Iah8 goa2 oe7 chau2 li7-khui li2, oe7 ouh.¡¨ 
  Hit si5, be2 jip i, i oat8-ke3 khi3 khoaN3 kong2, ¡§Chau2, chau2, khoaN3 li2 oe7 joa7 kin2. Li2 liah8 goa2 boe7 tioh8, goa2 si7 chit8 e5 kiuN-piaN2 lang5.¡¨ 
  Be2 liah8 i boe7 tioh8. 
  Bo5 joa7 ku2 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 kau3 ti7 chhek-chhng, u7 choe7-choe7 siak-tiu7 e5 lang5. Chiah-e5 lang5 phiN7-kiN3 chit e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 ai3 ka7 i liah8 lai5, kong2, ¡§Soe3-han3 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2, m7-thang chau2 hiah kin2, li2 khoaN3 liau2 chin ho2 chiah8.¡¨ 
  Chong2-si7 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-Na2 pi2 tai7-seng khah chhut-lat8 chau2, iah8 I chau2 e5 si5 kio3 kong2, ¡§Goa2 oe7 chau2 li7-khui chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5, chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 ta-pou-lang5, chit8 chiah gu5, koh chit8 chiah be2. Ia7 goa2 oe7 chau2 li7-khui lin2, oe7 ouh.¡¨ 
  Hit si5 i khoaN3-kiN3 i2-keng chau2 li7-khui siak-tiu7 e5 lang5, i oat8-ke3 khi3 khoaN3, toa7 siaN ka7 in kong2, ¡§Chau2, chau2, khoaN3 lin2 oe7 joa7 kin2. Lin2 liah8 goa2 boe7 tioh8, goa2 si7 chit8 e5 kiuN-piaN2 lang5.¡¨ 
  Iah8 siak-tiu7 e5 lang5 liah8 i boe7 tioh8. 
  Au7-lai5 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 pi2 tai7-seng chau2 khah kin2. I tit8-tit8 chau2, kau3 i kau3 chit8 khu chhan5, u7 choe7-choe7 koah-tiu7 e5 lang5. Hiah-e5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 i chin7 ho2 khoaN3, in jip i kio3 kong2, ¡§Theng3-hau7 chit8 e7 ! Theng3-hau7 chit8 e7, soe3-han3 kiuN-piaN2 gia2-na2 ! Gun2 ai3 chiah8 li2.¡¨ 
  Chong2-si7 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 pi2 tai7-seng khah chhut-lat8 chhio3, iah8 chhin-chhiuN7 hong tit8 chau2. 
  I kong2, ¡§Oh hou3 ! Oh hou3 ! Goa2 oe7 chau2 li7-khui chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5, chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 ta-pou-lang5, chit8 chiah gu5, chit8 chiah be2, koh chit8 e5 chhek-chhng e5 siak tiu7 e5 lang5. Iah8 goa2 oe7 chau2 li7-khui lin2 oe7 ouh.¡¨ 
  Hit si5 i khoaN3-kiN3 i u7 chau2 chhut hiah-e5 koah-tiu7 e5 lang5, i oat8-ke3 khi3 khoaN3, toa7 siaN ka7 in kong2, ¡§Chau2, chau2, khoaN3 lin2 oe7 joa7 kin2. Lin2 liah8 goa2 boe7 tioh8, goa2 si7 chit8 e5 kiuN-piaN2 lang5.¡¨ Iah8 chiah-e5 koah-tiu7 e5 lang5 liah8 i boe7 tioh8. 
  Tui3 chit si5 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 chin7 khui3-thau5, si7 i siuN7 bo5 lang5 liah8 i oe7 tioh8. Tu2-tu2 hit-tiap8 i khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 chiah hou5-li5 tui3 chhan5-nih8 teh ke3-lai5. Hou5-li5 khoaN3-kiN3 i chiu7 chau2-lai5. Chong2-si7 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 toa7 siaN ka7 i kong2, ¡§Li2 liah8 goa2 boe7 tioh8.¡¨ Hou5-li5 chiu7 chau2 khah kin2, kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 iah8 chau2 khah kin2, i teh chau2 e5 si5 chhio3-chhio3 kong2, ¡§Goa2 oe7 chau2 li7-khui chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5, chit8 e5 soe3-han3 e5 lau7 ta-pou-lang5, chit8 chiah gu5, chit8 chiah be2, chit8 e5 chhek-chhng e5 siak-tiu7 e5 lang5, koh chit8 e5 chhan5-nih8 e5 koah-tiu7 e5 lang5. Iah8 goa2 oe7 chau2 li7-khui li2, oe7 ouh. Chau2, chau2, khoaN3 li2 oe7 joa7 kin2. Li2 liah8 goa2 boe7 tioh8, goa2 si7 chit8 e5 kiuN-piaN2 lang5.¡¨ 
  Hou5-li5 kong2, ¡§Mih-tai7, goa2 na7 oe7 iah8 bo5 beh liah8 li2. Goa2 bo5 siuN7 beh kiau2-jiau2 li2.¡¨ 
  Tu2-tu2 hit si5, chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 kau3 ti7 chit8 tiau5 khoe. I boe7 siu5 ke3-khi3, iah8 i ai3 chau2 li7-khui gu5, be2 kap lang5. 
  Hou5-li5 kong2, ¡§Thiau3 ti7 goa2 e5 be2, goa2 beh chai3 li2 ke3-khi3.¡¨ Sou2-i2 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 thiau3 ti7 hou5-li5 e5 be2, iah8 hou5-li5 siu5 jip8 khoe. Li7 hoaN7 bo5 joa7 hng7, i oat8-thau5 kong2, ¡§Soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2, li2 ti7 goa2 e5 be2 siuN tang7, kiaN-liau2 li2 oe7 phah tam5. Thiau3 tiam3 goa2 e5 ka-chiah.¡¨ 
  Chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 chiu7 thiau3 tiam3 hou5-li5 e5 ka-chiah. Koh khah khi3 tam7-poh8, hou5-li5 kong2, ¡§Goa2 kiaN-liau2 chui2 beh im-tioh8 li2 ; thiau3 tiam3 goa2 e5 keng-thau5.¡¨ 
  Chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 chiu7 thiau3 ti7 i e5 keng-thau5. 
  Kau3 ti7 khoe-tiong, hou5-li5 kong2, ¡§Chham2 lah, soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2, goa2 e5 keng-thau5 si7 chim3-tioh8; thiau3 tiam3 goa2 e5 phiN7 goa2 chiah oe7 hou7 li2 li7 chui2. ¡¨ 
  Sou2-i2 chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 thiau3 ti7 i e5 phiN7. 
  Tu2-tu2 hou5-li5 kau3 ti7 hoaN7 e5 si5, i thau5 kiu chit8 e7, ka7 i sahN chit8 e7. 
  Chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gin2-na2 kong2, ¡§Ai ah ! Goa2 khi3 si3 hun chit8 lah !¡¨ Koh chit8 siaN i kong2, ¡§HaN5, goa2 khi3 chit8 poaN3 lah !¡¨ Iu7 koh chit8 siaN kong2, ¡§Goa2 siN3-mia7 ! Goa2 khi3 si3 hun saN lah !¡¨ Hit-tiap8 liau2-au7, chit e5 soe3-han3 e5 kiuN-piaN2 gia2-na2 long2 bo5 koh kong2 chit8 ku3. 
  (1) Mng7. KiuN-piaN2 ang-a2 u7 gau5 chau2 a2 bo5 ? U7, gu5, be2, kap kui2-na7 lang5 long2 liah8 I boe7 tioh8. 
  (2) Au7-lai5 chaiN2-iuN7 hou7 Hou5-li5 chiah8 khi3 ? In-ui7 hou5-li5 eng7 khui2-khiat e5 pou7 lai5 phian3 i. 
  Seng3-keng kong2, ¡§Soe3-kiaN2 ah, phaiN2-lang5 in2-iu2 lin2 m7-thang than3 i.¡¨ Chim-gian5 1 chiuN 10 chat. 
  Koh kong2, ¡§Hou7 lan2 bo5 choe3 gin2-na2, tiong3-tioh8 lang5 khui2-khiat e5 ke3, kap khi-phian3 e5 hoat-sut8, hou7 it-chhe3 pat8 kau3 e5 hong io5-tang7, chhe-lai5 chhe-khi3, than3 tak8 hang7 e5 iN7-toan.¡¨ I2-hut-sou2 4 chiuN 14 chat. 
  Soe3 Chiah Long5 kap Sai
  Bat u7 chit8 e5 toa7 e5 chhiu7-na5, ti7 chit e5 chhiu7-na5 u7 chit8 chiah toa7 chiah sai chiu7-si7 chhiu7-na5 e5 ong5. Put-lun7 sim2-mih8 si5 i ai3 chiah8, chiu7 tui3 toe7-nih8 e5 chioh8-tong7 chhut-lai5 chhut siaN hau2. I hau2 kui2 siaN, long2-chong2 chiah-e5 soe3 chiah-e5 siu3 chin7 kiaN, sou2-i2 in tui3 in e5 khang chhut-lai5,chau2 chia, chau2 hia, lai5 siam2-pi7. Chong2-si7 sai oe7 khoaN3-kiN3 in ti7 ta2-loh8. Iah8 i sahN in, hai7-si2 in, ka7 in thun-loh8-khi3. 
  I siong5-siong5 an2-ni choe3, kau3 lou7-be2 bo5 chit8 hang7 mih8 oah8 ti7 chhiu7-na5, chi2-u7 chhun sai kap nng7 chiah long5, chit8 chiah soe3 chiah long5-pe7, kap chit8 chiah soe3 chiah long5-bu2. 
  In chau2 chin7 choe7 pai2 kau3 chin7 san2 chin7 sian7, iah8 boe7 koh chau2 khah kin2. U7 chit8 jit8 sai chin7 kun7, chit chiah long5-bu2 chin7 kiaN kong2, ¡§Ai ! Long5-pe7 ! Long5-pe7 ! Goa2 siuN7 lan2 e5 si5 kau3 lah ! Sai tek-khak oe7 ka7-tioh8 lan2.¡¨ 
  Long5-pe7 kong2, ¡§Chheh ! Gong7, Gong7 ! Long5-bu2 ! Lai5, lan2 koh chau2 chit8 te3-a2 !¡¨ 
  In chiu7 tit8-tit8 chau2 chin7 kin2, iah8 hit pai2 sai liah8 in bo5 tioh8. 
  Chong2-si7 ti7 lou7-be2 u7 chit8 jit8 sai lai5 koh khah kun7 e5 si5, iah8 soe3 chiah long5-bu2 chin7 kiaN kau3 beh si2. I toa7 siaN kong2, ¡§Ai, Long5-pe7, Long5-pe7 ! Goa2 siuN7 lan2 e5 si5 tek-khak kau3 lah ! Chit pai2 sai oe7 chiah8 lan2.¡¨ 
  Chit chiah soe3 chiah long5-pe7 kong2, ¡§Bo5, long5-bu2, m7 bian2 hoan5-lo2 ! Li2 chiau3 goa2 sou2 ka7 li2 kong2 e5 choe3; chiu7 bo5 tai7-chi3.¡¨ 
  Hit si5 hiah-e5 kau2-koai3 e5 soe3 chiah long5 sou2 choe3 e5, chiu7-si7 saN khan chhiu2 lai5 kau3 ti7 sai e5 sou2-chai7, tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 in e5 i3-su3 ai3 kap i saN-kap tiam3. 
  Sai khoaN3-kiN3 in lai5, khia7 khi2-lai5, hau2 chit8 siaN chin7 hiong5, iah8 kong2, ¡§Lin2 chiah-e5 phaiN2-mia7 mih8 ! Liam5-piN beh hou7 goa2 ka7 lin2 chiah8 khi3 ! Lin2 chaiN2-iuN7 bo5 khah cha2 lai5 ?¡¨ 
  Long5-pe7 thau5 aN3 kau3 chin7 chhih kong2, ¡§Si7 ouh, Sai-pe7, gun2 pun2 khah cha2 beh lai5; gun2 chai gun2 eng-kai tioh8 lai5; gun2 iah8 ai3 lai5; chong2-si7 tak8 pai2 gun2 khi2-sin beh lai5, chiu7 u7 chit8 chiah chin7 hiong5 e5 toa7 chiah sai tui3 chhiu7-na5 chhut-lai5, hau2, hou7 gun2 kiaN, sou2-i2 gun2 chau2-khi3.¡¨ 
  Chit chiah sai, toa7 siaN hau2, kong2, ¡§Li2 teh kong2 sim2-mih8 ? Bo5 pat8 chiah sai ti7 chit e5 chhiu7-na5, li2 chai mah ?¡¨ 
  Soe3 chiah long5 kong2, ¡§U7-iaN2, u7-iaN2, Sai-pe7, Goa2 chai pat8 lang5 iah8 phah-sng3 an2-an2; chong2-si7 sit8-chai7 u7 koh chit8 chiah sai. I e5 khah toa7 li2 chhin-chhiuN7 li2 e5 khah toa7 goa2 chit8 iuN7. I e5 bin7 si7 ke chin7 hiong5, iah8 i e5 hau2 e5 siaN si7 koh khah thang kiaN. Aih8 ! i si7 pi2 li2 ke joa7 thang kiaN leh !¡¨ 
  Tui3 an2-ni chit chiah sai khia7 khi2-lai5 hau2 kau3 chhiu7-na5 oe7 choah. I kong2, ¡§Chhoa7 goa2 khi3 chhe7 chit chiah sai. Goa2 beh chiah8 i, iah8 au7-lai5 beh chiah8 lin2.¡¨
  Chiah-e5 soe3 chiah long5 thiau3 khi3 thau5-cheng5, iah8 sai kiaN5 ti7 au7-bin7. In chhoa7 I kau3 chit8 e5 sou2-chai7, u7 chit8 e5 iN5 koh chhim e5 chiN2, u7 chheng e5 chui2. In seh8 ti7 chit peng5, sai khia7 ti7 hit peng5. 
  Soe3 chiah long5 kong2, ¡§Sai-pe7, i tiam3 ti7 hia lah ! I ti7 e7-toe2 !¡¨ 
  Sai lai5 kun7-oa2 khoaN3 tui3 chui2 loh8-khi3, iah8 koh chit8 chiah sai e5 bin7 tui3 chui2-lai7 khoaN3 chhut-lai5. 
  I khoaN3-kiN3 an2-ni koh toa7 siaN hau2, io5 i e5 chang, iah8 chhui3-khi2 giang3-giang3. Chui2-lai7 e5 sai iah8 io5 i e5 chang, giang3 i e5 chhui3-khi2. 
  Teng2-bin7 chit chiah sai koh io5 i e5 chang, hm7-hm7 hau2, iah8 tian2 chit8 e5 hiong5 e5 bin7. Chong2-si7 chui2-lai7 e5 sai iah8 tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, lai5 oh8 i. Teng2-bin7 chit chiah sai tong3 boe7 tiau5. I chiu7 thiau3 loh8 chiN2-lai7, jip hit chiah sai. 
  Chong2-si7 li2 tek-khak chai bo5 koh pat8 chiah sai, chi2-u7 si7 chui2 to3-chio3 e5 siong7 na7-tiaN7. 
  Sou2-i2 chit chiah kho2-lin5 e5 lau7 sai leng3-lai5, leng3-khi3, boe7 tit thang chiuN7 kia7-kia7 e5 chiN2-piN, i chiu7 chim3-si2. 
  I chim3-si2 liau2, chiah-e5 soe3 chiah long5 saN khan chhiu2, na2 thiau3 na2 seh8 chit e5 chiN2, iah8 chhiuN3 kong2, ¡§Sai si2 lah ! Sai si2 lah ! Gun2 u7 hai7-si2 beh hai7 gun2 hit chiah sai ! Sai si2 lah ! Sai si2 lah ! Hoh! hoh ! hoh !¡¨ 
  (1) Mng7. Chhiu7-na5 lai7 te7 it beng2 e5 siu3 si7 sim2-mih8 ? Sai. 
  (2) Sai chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 poah8-loh8 chui2 ? In-ui7 kiau-ngou7, ti3-kau3 gong7-gong7 tiong3 tioh8 long5 e5 ke3. 
  Seng3-keng kong2, ¡§Choan-bu7 kin2-sin7, chhi5-siu2, keng2-seng2, in-ui7 lin2 e5 tui3-tek8 Mou5-kui2, chhin-chhiuN7 hau2 e5 sai si3-koe3 kiaN5, chhe7 thang thun-ka7 e5 lang5.¡¨ Pi2-tek chian5-su 5 chiuN 8 chat. 
  Koh kong2, ¡§PhaiN2-lang5 e5 lou7, chhin-chhiuN7 ou-am3, ka-ki7 m7 chai in-ui7 sim2-mih8 Poah8-to2.¡¨ Chim-gian5 4 chiuN 19 chat. 
